<p source="SHANGBO.SHILIUZIWEN 9.59.1 (STRIPS 1, 12) MACHENGYUAN 9: 273, 288 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-1a.1">[...] 其[.]之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-1a.2">史留曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-1a.3">"留也,  故齊邦敝吏之子也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-1a.4">亡女[茹=make plans?]圖也. [...] [1]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-1a.5">[...] "聞子之言大懼,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-1a.6">不知所為 "</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-1a.7">夫子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-1a.8">"善哉!</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-1a.9">臨事而懼，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-1a.10">此不…[12]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.SHILIUZIWEN 9.59.2 (STRIP 2) MACHENGYUAN 9: 274 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-2a.1">[...]  既(死?)之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-2a.2">以其子,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-2a.3">子其身(信?)之貳(惑?)也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-2a.4">今使子師之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-2a.5">君之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-2a.6">擇之慎矣. [2]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.SHILIUZIWEN 9.59.3 (STRIPS 6-7,11) MACHENGYUAN 9: 279-281, 287 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.1">[...] 也.” [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.2">史蒥曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.3">“何謂八?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.4">夫子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.5">“內邪偽，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.6">幽色与酒，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.7">大鐘鼎，【6】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.8">美宮室,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.9">驅軹畋獵，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.10">舉訟獄，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.11">此所以失，【7】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-3a.12">不可以弗戒.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.SHILIUZIWEN 9.59.4 (STRIPS 11, 3, 10) MACHENGYUAN 9: 287, 275, 285 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.1">子之事行，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.2">百姓得其利，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.3">邦家以𢕌[夷]，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.4">子之事不行，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.5">百姓 [...]【11】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.6">[...] 必[在]危其邦家，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.7">則能貴[潰]於禹湯，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.8">禹湯則學，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.9">自始【3】有民以來，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.10">未或能才立[=栽粒, or =在立]於地之上，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.11">一或不免有禍，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-4a.12">不 [...]【10】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.SHILIUZIWEN 9.59.5 (STRIPS 9, 8) MACHENGYUAN 9: 284, 282 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-5a.1">史蒥曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-5a.2">“何謂信，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-5a.3">何謂【9】敬?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-5a.4">夫子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-5a.5">“敬也者, 瞻人之顏色</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-5a.6">而為之為，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-5a.7">視其所欲而 [...]”【8】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.SHILIUZIWEN 9.59.6 (STRIPS 6.31 strip 25, 5, 4) MACHENGYUAN 6: 223, 207">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-6a.1">[…]民氓不可侮</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-6a.2">衆之所植，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-6a.3">莫之能廢也；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-6a.4">衆之 X [上六•孔25]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-6a.5">莫之能豎也 [史5] [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-6a.6">極聽 (常啟?)</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0087_tls_001-6a.7">同(通) 古,</seg>
                </p>

</div>
